00:40:44,920 --> 00:40:45,800
Remember?

516
00:40:47,760 --> 00:40:48,760
Yeah.

517
00:40:50,040 --> 00:40:51,560
[typewriter clacking]

518
00:40:56,360 --> 00:40:57,480
[Lizzie] This arrived.

519
00:40:58,440 --> 00:40:59,840
It's from the sanatorium.

520
00:41:01,600 --> 00:41:03,560
I've already paid Ruby's medical bills.

521
00:41:04,920 --> 00:41:06,240
I don't think it's a bill.

522
00:41:06,840 --> 00:41:08,160
It says it's urgent.

523
00:41:08,240 --> 00:41:09,760
From the senior consultant.

524
00:41:10,960 --> 00:41:12,480
[typewriter clacking]

525
00:41:29,120 --> 00:41:30,840
Why didn't you come to bed?

526
00:41:36,040 --> 00:41:37,800
Why didn't you come to bed?

527
00:41:37,880 --> 00:41:39,160
[typing stops]

528
00:41:43,600 --> 00:41:45,880
I'm typing up
my recollection of the meeting.

529
00:41:47,400 --> 00:41:49,480
If I... If I do it straight away,

530
00:41:50,640 --> 00:41:52,320
I can quote people word for word.

531
00:41:53,960 --> 00:41:58,720
The information is more useful
to Mr Churchill if it is word for word.

532
00:42:00,400 --> 00:42:01,560
[typewriter clacking]

533
00:42:05,200 --> 00:42:06,040
[exhales]

534
00:42:26,200 --> 00:42:27,280
I burnt her chair.

535
00:42:27,360 --> 00:42:28,360
[sobbing softly]

536
00:42:30,120 --> 00:42:32,400
The paint on the wood
left a smell in the air.

537
00:42:33,840 --> 00:42:35,000
I didn't open the window.

538
00:42:37,560 --> 00:42:38,720
I quite like the smell.

539
00:42:43,400 --> 00:42:44,720
[sobbing]

540
00:43:05,280 --> 00:43:10,320
[Tommy] Not yet. Not yet.

541
00:43:13,280 --> 00:43:17,440
I have this work to do
'cause now I know that I will change.

542
00:43:20,040 --> 00:43:21,160
That I have to change.

543
00:43:23,200 --> 00:43:25,840
And change for good, Lizzie.

544
00:43:31,520 --> 00:43:32,520
Not just yet.

545
00:43:44,680 --> 00:43:45,600
[typing continues]

546
00:43:51,760 --> 00:43:53,160
[distant telephone ringing]

547
00:44:04,520 --> 00:44:05,480
Hello?

548
00:44:09,800 --> 00:44:10,800
Oh.

549
00:44:11,560 --> 00:44:12,760
[both breathing heavily]

550
00:44:24,760 --> 00:44:26,760
["Do You Love Me?" playing]

551
00:44:27,440 --> 00:44:30,160
<i>♪ She had a heart
Full of love and devotion ♪</i>

552
00:44:31,240 --> 00:44:34,200
<i>♪ She had a mind full
